{"id": 696, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在喝茶这件事上都有哪些习惯？", "description": "说起来，你是连喝下午茶的时候都不喝茶的人吗？", "record_count": 3866, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201606071944020tHZNXJDKrlsGwc7.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-12-12T08:19:21Z", "options": [{"id": 33792, "content": "工作的时候只能简单冲泡一下～冬季喜欢红茶和茉莉花～不过还是周末喜欢和老公一起泡茶喝", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323781}, {"id": 34048, "content": "会根据节气，心情选择最近要喝的茶。如果是红茶，心情好的时候还会配奶和糖，喜欢尝试很多不同地方的不同品种。茶包是万不得已才喝的。紧张和生气的时候感觉一杯茶可以让人快速镇定下来。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 357697}, {"id": 33793, "content": "茶具整齐干净，不然喝不下", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 342989}, {"id": 34305, "content": "夏天喝 冬则眠", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 315426}, {"id": 33794, "content": "因为不懂，每次人家问喝什么我都会说:来一杯菊花……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 163696}, {"id": 34050, "content": "就是茶包，也喜欢自己家弄的茶叶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 357715}, {"id": 33795, "content": "喝茶！多种含义呦！纪检部门请你去配合调查好像是也叫喝茶……哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 354854}, {"id": 352260, "content": "喝", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1602264}, {"id": 36100, "content": "功夫茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 376860}, {"id": 33798, "content": "除了喝茶，别的都不喝，泡一杯茶，圣过一切", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 64497}, {"id": 34054, "content": "一杯茶泡一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222140}, {"id": 34055, "content": "高山茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156150}, {"id": 34312, "content": "最近爱喝普洱，浓郁，醇香，厚重。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 350367}, {"id": 36360, "content": "咬吸管", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 101526}, {"id": 36362, "content": "日照绿，茉莉花最爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 380329}, {"id": 34059, "content": "早晨吃的那个茶叶蛋吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 357857}, {"id": 33804, "content": "明前第一波高山云雾茶，一支烟，音乐，还可以写写钢笔字！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215872}, {"id": 34061, "content": "方式太传统，如果有一种新方式就OK了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133297}, {"id": 34062, "content": "用沾满茶锈的杯子喝起来更香", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 332015}, {"id": 34063, "content": "饭后一杯茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 332015}, {"id": 33553, "content": "下午茶难道不是咖啡冰激凌蛋糕吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 313, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 350163}, {"id": 33554, "content": "附庸风雅的时候，大吉岭+奶。不喜欢加糖。更多的时候就是家里有什么茶喝什么茶，纯粹是喝白水嘴里没味儿才会喝茶的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279916}, {"id": 33810, "content": "保温杯泡茶然后倒出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 306034}, {"id": 36626, "content": "没有习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 382454}, {"id": 33811, "content": "希望杯子里的咖啡喝不完！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 354965}, {"id": 34323, "content": "不喝茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178075}, {"id": 33556, "content": "周一铁观音，周二龙井，周三大麦，周四苦荞，周五牛蒡，周六普洱。柜子里满满的茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 222, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 203555}, {"id": 34580, "content": "不同的茶叶，必须配合不同的水温，尤其是龙井，非常注重汤色，所以必须水温在85℃左右", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 363107}, {"id": 33557, "content": "饭后喝普洱减肥是骗人的喂！", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305410}, {"id": 33558, "content": "一般早上起来喝完一杯温水，会泡一壶铁观音喝，个人觉得可以精神点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 352468}, {"id": 34070, "content": "喜欢喝 懒得泡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 357991}, {"id": 33559, "content": "万年的车仔红茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 4770}, {"id": 34327, "content": "来一杯茶香，安神怡心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360258}, {"id": 33560, "content": "喜欢自己煮茶喝。 首先要将饼茶研碎待用。然后开始煮水。以精选佳水置釜中，以炭火烧开。但不能全沸，加入茶末。茶与水交融，二沸时出现沫饽，沫为细小茶花，饽为大花，皆为茶之精华。此时将沫饽杓出，置熟盂之中，以备用。继续烧煮，茶与水进一步融合，波滚浪涌，称为三沸。此时将二沸时盛出之沫饽浇烹茶的水与茶，视人数多寡而严格量入。茶汤煮好，均匀的斟入各人碗中，包含雨露均施，", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 352481}, {"id": 33816, "content": "饱饭后隔半小时后喝茶，一个人喝的是生活感。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 354976}, {"id": 35352, "content": "只喝红茶拿铁", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155115}, {"id": 33562, "content": "泡一大杯，牛人牛饮。", "image": null, "praise_count": 456, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 352488}, {"id": 33563, "content": "作为学生党不喝就会犯困", "image": null, "praise_count": 70, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236230}, {"id": 33564, "content": "饮茶谁关心喝什么，主要在陪你聊天的人吧～", "image": null, "praise_count": 146, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141748}, {"id": 34076, "content": "康师傅绿茶有瘾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 358019}, {"id": 33565, "content": "英伯伦的果味都可以", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139738}, {"id": 33566, "content": "奶茶与蛋糕。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 314483}, {"id": 33567, "content": "喜欢功夫茶，也喜欢大壶茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5005}, {"id": 34079, "content": "coffee党", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 261769}, {"id": 33568, "content": "觉得喝茶麻烦的肯定不止我一个?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 302316}, {"id": 33824, "content": "乌龙茶是最好喝的茶！一喝就上瘾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 55249}, {"id": 34080, "content": "喜欢和认真对待我泡的茶的人一块喝茶", "image": "img/option/option/201607022007582HxBUe3LRCtuDv90.jpg", "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 327226}, {"id": 34081, "content": "随便喝啦，好不好\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 358057}, {"id": 33570, "content": "经常换着喝，不挑剔，喜欢自己给自己一个人泡", "image": null, "praise_count": 436, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 348081}, {"id": 34082, "content": "第一道想倒掉，又嫌第二道太淡。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 358061}]}